Class Association

  • java.lang.Object
    • tdam.Association

  • public class Association
extends java.lang.Object
    Class for an association in the network.

    An association stores an id to identify it, stores the source unit and the destination unit (i.e. connected units), and has a strength.

    Author:
    Matthias Keysermann
